    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, Storegga, Froeyabank and Area from Storegga-Haltenbank to Greenwich meridian, 30 September 02:00 UTC to 30 September 15:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>One or several polar lows develop in E3 and Deep E4, and will move southwards. During early Monday morning to Monday forenoon they are expected to reach Storegge-Haltenbank. Occasionally north gale force, possibly strong gale force 9 is expected west of the centre. The polar low is expected to weaken Monday afternoon.</description>
    <instruction>Be aware of abrupt weather changes.</instruction>
